{"tid":1752594,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[正視聽]聽日當選區議員一定要去poly表態","createTime":"2019-11-24T22:00:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-25T00:51:46.000Z","uid":266548,"like":5,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"6212b7737c37d91e1918ad724c181d8b2c554cc4","tid":1752594,"uid":266548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T22:00:33.000Z","msg":"區議員當選係唔洗宣誓。<br />\n係唔犯法既前提底下，一定要全部當選區議員去poly。<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">poly有手足等區選等人救等到就輕生，投左咁多人出來就係為左救手足。</span></span></strong><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">有手足先有議席，無議席但有手足都可以，但為議席無手足就點都唔得。</span></span></strong><br />\n如果為保議席同利益就唔做野，咁到底選來為咩？淨係有政治立場但無行動實踐都接受到？<br />\n幾多人用五大訴求既名義去選？其中一項係釋放被捕人士啊，poly手足同比狗軟禁無分別。<br />\n總之聽日要見到當選區議員一定要去poly救手足，唔洗衝，淨係用盡合法方法去救就好好。<br />\n為救手足咩方法都要試。<br />\n唔做既當選區議員，你同梁耀忠無分別。"},{"pid":"b69243e660c32998fcb3a7dcd4e9785a52f892e6","tid":1752594,"uid":266548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T22:02:42.000Z","msg":"ｐｕｓｈ"},{"pid":"095ac50e3a71aa7ff48b1aee1cc13279d0666899","tid":1752594,"uid":266548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T22:04:52.000Z","msg":"ｐｉｓｈ"},{"pid":"dc86786a1e3fb1d00ba5e2da6a3f5afbaa674c67","tid":1752594,"uid":4062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T22:05:06.000Z","msg":"推，唔救手足，<br />\n咁販民係咪即係又食多次人血饅頭？<br />\n一定唔可以俾佢哋再多次出賣香港人。"},{"pid":"5b7ddb198538806225035ecde2817ba41090720a","tid":1752594,"uid":7270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T22:05:07.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"20d96481e4efb834e1ef81ae4227b0a960560551","tid":1752594,"uid":7270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T22:05:30.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4c8a8d69369d106847eb0210701f327e01932b4e","tid":1752594,"uid":7270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T22:06:39.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a0714829e91da3f49f4c702309ad